<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport">
    <title>About Us - Your Application</title>
    <link href="~/assets/vendor/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="~/assets/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        .main {
            padding: 60px 0;
        }
        .main h1 {
            color: green;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .main h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .main p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .section-title {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .section-content {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<main id="main" class="main">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title text-center">
        </div>
         <div class="section-content">
            <h1>Welcome to Local In Istanbul</h1>
            <p>At Local In Istanbul, our mission is to inspire and guide you through the hidden gems of this magnificent city. Istanbul, with its rich history, vibrant culture, and diverse culinary scene, offers a treasure trove of experiences waiting to be discovered. Our platform is dedicated to showcasing the best local restaurants, coffee shops, and unique spots that define the true essence of Istanbul.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="section-content">
            <h1>Discover the Heart of Istanbul</h1>
            <h2>Unearth Hidden Gems</h2>
            <p>We believe that the soul of Istanbul lies in its local places. From quaint coffee houses tucked away in historic alleyways to family-run restaurants serving age-old recipes, we bring you closer to the authentic Istanbul experience. Each place we feature has been handpicked for its charm, quality, and connection to the city's heritage.</p>
            <h2>Taste the Tradition</h2>
            <p>Istanbul is a culinary paradise, offering flavors that tell stories of the past and present. Our curated selection of eateries includes a variety of options that showcase traditional Turkish cuisine as well as innovative modern dishes. Whether you're a foodie on the hunt for the best kebab or a coffee enthusiast looking for the perfect brew, Local In Istanbul has got you covered.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="section-content">
            <h1>Our Vision</h1>
            <h2>Celebrating Local Culture</h2>
            <p>Local In Istanbul is more than just a guide; it's a celebration of the city's local culture. We aim to highlight the passion and craftsmanship of local business owners who make Istanbul a unique and vibrant place. By promoting these local establishments, we hope to support the community and encourage sustainable tourism.</p>
            <h2>Inspiring Connections</h2>
            <p>We believe in the power of shared experiences. Our platform not only helps you find the best places but also connects you with stories and insights from locals and fellow travelers. Through our detailed information and reviews, we aim to create a community of explorers who appreciate and respect the rich tapestry of Istanbul's local scene.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="section-content">
            <h1>Join Us on This Journey</h1>
            <p>Whether you're a local looking for new spots or a traveler eager to explore Istanbul beyond the usual tourist attractions, Local In Istanbul is here to guide you. We invite you to join us on this journey of discovery and inspiration. Let’s uncover the magic of Istanbul, one local place at a time.</p>
            <p>Stay inspired, stay curious, and embrace the local charm of Istanbul with us.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>

<script src="~/assets/vendor/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
